skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: we are family
des: A collection of Burns to show your family that even though you love them they can be a little annoying sometimes. Ask your device to open we are family and continue saying yes to Alexis prompts until you’ve had enough. Use this to trick your family and friends if they have been giving you a little too much grief.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
